-among-top-indian-firms-with-significant-middle-east-exposure-ws-l-9937670.html","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-03-02T12:30:24","source":"News 18"},{"id":"816147951995515264","title":"Kalyan Jewellers generates 12% of revenue from West Asia.","summary":"Kalyan Jewellers generates 12% of revenue from West Asia.","url":"https://sqst.in/shareMessage?msgId=816147951995515262","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-03-02T08:50:35","source":"ScoutQuest"},{"id":"514106","title":"Indian stocks like L&T, Kalyan Jewellers, KEC International, and Welspun Corp have substantial Middle East exposure.\nProjects include desalination, infrastructure, and transmission, with L&T's 49% intl orders, KEC's Q4 bids, and Welspun's $1.7k cr capex.","summary":"Indian stocks like L&T, Kalyan Jewellers, KEC International, and Welspun Corp have substantial Middle East exposure.\nProjects include desalination, infrastructure, and transmission, with L&T's 49% intl orders, KEC's Q4 bids, and Welspun's $1.7k cr capex.","url":"https://www.cnbctv18.com/market/iran-conflict-indian-stocks-middle-east-exposure-larsen-kec-wabag-sw-renewables-kec-kalyan-share-price-19860235.htm","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-03-01T17:39:42","source":"CNBC TV 18"},{"id":"260219157106231","title":"Titan posted 40% YoY revenue growth in Q3, driven by 32% like-to-like growth. Kalyan Jewellers saw 42% YoY growth, supported by 27% same-store sales growth.\nDespite gold price volatility, demand remained strong into Jan 2026. Jewellery led consumer discretionary growth, aided by festive season and higher-ticket purchases.","summary":"Titan posted 40% YoY revenue growth in Q3, driven by 32% like-to-like growth. Kalyan Jewellers saw 42% YoY growth, supported by 27% same-store sales growth.\nDespite gold price volatility, demand remained strong into Jan 2026. Jewellery led consumer discretionary growth, aided by festive season and higher-ticket purchases.","url":"https://www.financialexpress.com/business/news/why-jewellery-retailers-had-a-standout-q3-despite-big-swing-in-gold-prices-titan-kalyan-keep-the-momentumnbsp/4148484/","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-19T16:58:27","source":"Financial Express"},{"id":"501341","title":"Kalyan Jewellers promoter acquired 4.65 lakh shares, total since Feb 9 is 9.25 lakh.","summary":"Kalyan Jewellers promoter acquired 4.65 lakh shares, total since Feb 9 is 9.25 lakh.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-17T13:05:52","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"479121","title":"Kalyan Jewellers alerts SEBI about alleged market manipulation concerns.\nThe company seeks suspension from the Futures and Options (F&O) segment.","summary":"Kalyan Jewellers alerts SEBI about alleged market manipulation concerns.\nThe company seeks suspension from the Futures and Options (F&O) segment.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-09T11:28:08","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"478859","title":"Kalyan Jewellers plans 6-7 annual overseas showrooms, with growth tied to Arab franchise talks.\nIndia's maintenance capex is INR 175 Cr, with 30-40 Candere stores costing INR 2-2.5 Cr each.","summary":"Kalyan Jewellers plans 6-7 annual overseas showrooms, with growth tied to Arab franchise talks.\nIndia's maintenance capex is INR 175 Cr, with 30-40 Candere stores costing INR 2-2.5 Cr each.","url":"","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-09T08:50:33","source":"Livesquawk"},{"id":"475823","title":"Kalyan Jewellers India Ltd approves incorporation of a wholly-owned subsidiary, KJG Brands Private Limited, focused on regional jewellery retail.\nThe subsidiary will align with Kalyan Jewellers' business, with incorporation subject to regulatory approvals.","summary":"Kalyan Jewellers India Ltd approves incorporation of a wholly-owned subsidiary, KJG Brands Private Limited, focused on regional jewellery retail.\nThe subsidiary will align with Kalyan Jewellers' business, with incorporation subject to regulatory approvals.","url":"https://www.bseindia.com/stockinfo/AnnPdfOpen.aspx?Pname=4a47909a-916a-4